<h2>Tipping</h2>

<p>
  DJ Sprenk takes payment on
  <a href="{{ site.social.paypal }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
    >PayPal (@djsprenk)<span class="sr-only"> (opens in a new tab)</span></a
  >
  or
  <a href="{{ site.social.venmo }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
    >Venmo (@djsprenk)<span class="sr-only"> (opens in a new tab)</span></a
  >.
</p>

<p>
  The sets are free to enjoy for personal use and at free community events, so tips are appreciated but never required
  in these instances!
</p>

<h3>When it's <em>required</em></h3>

<p>Playing a mixed set at an event with any sort of fee? You should be tipping your DJ!</p>

<p>
  See the <a href="/policies">Music Usage Policies</a> for DJ Sprenk's specific details on where tipping is required and
  for recommended tip amounts.
</p>

<h2>Patreon</h2>

<p>
