    >Patreon (@DJSprenk)<span class="sr-only"> (opens in a new tab)</span></a
  >
  to get early access to sets and behind-the-scenes updates.
</p>

<h2>Events, Commissions, or Private Lessons</h2>

<p>Hire DJ Sprenk for an event, commission a custom set, or book for a private lesson.</p>

